high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and take a step forward, turn left again and walk over to the counter then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the wooden bowl off of the counter.
Walk over to the fridge on your right.
Put the wooden bowl in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold then take it out.
Turn right and walk up to the wooden table, then walk to the microwave on the counter to your right.
Put the chilled wooden bowl in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wooden bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the brown bowl that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk a step forward and turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the microwave that's in front of you to your left and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right, then right again and move to the far counter.
Pick up the bowl from the front of the counter.
Carry the bowl and take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bowl inside. Shut the door and then open the door. Take out the bowl and shut the door.
Carry the bowl and turn around and locate the microwave across the room.
Open the microwave and place the bowl inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bowl and place it in the microwave.
